{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":713,"text":"I'm going to be showing some of the cybercriminals'"},{"time":2345,"text":"latest and nastiest creations."},{"time":4807,"text":"So basically, please don't go and download"},{"time":7715,"text":"any of the viruses that I show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10411,"text":"Some of you might be wondering what a cybersecurity specialist looks like,"},{"time":13429,"text":"and I thought I'd give you a quick insight"},{"time":15598,"text":"into my career so far."},{"time":18276,"text":"It's a pretty accurate description."},{"time":20777,"text":"This is what someone that specializes"},{"time":22433,"text":"in malware and hacking looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24853,"text":"So today, computer viruses and trojans,"},{"time":28267,"text":"designed to do everything from stealing data"},{"time":31147,"text":"to watching you in your webcam"},{"time":33188,"text":"to the theft of billions of dollars."},{"time":35966,"text":"Some malicious code today goes as far"},{"time":38161,"text":"as targeting power, utilities and infrastructure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42304,"text":"Let me give you a quick snapshot"},{"time":44265,"text":"of what malicious code is capable of today."},{"time":46879,"text":"Right now, every second, eight new users"},{"time":49949,"text":"are joining the Internet."},{"time":52104,"text":"Today, we will see 250,000 individual new computer viruses."},{"time":59412,"text":"We will see 30,000 new infected websites."},{"time":65185,"text":"And, just to kind of tear down a myth here,"},{"time":67271,"text":"lots of people think that when you get infected"},{"time":69759,"text":"with a computer virus, it's because you went to a porn site."},{"time":73210,"text":"Right? Well, actually, statistically speaking,"},{"time":75653,"text":"if you only visit porn sites, you're safer."},{"time":78778,"text":"People normally write that down, by the way. (Laughter)"},{"time":81780,"text":"Actually, about 80 percent of these"},{"time":83342,"text":"are small business websites getting infected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86855,"text":"Today's cybercriminal, what do they look like?"},{"time":89140,"text":"Well, many of you have the image, don't you,"},{"time":91566,"text":"of the spotty teenager sitting in a basement,"},{"time":93742,"text":"hacking away for notoriety."},{"time":96130,"text":"But actually today, cybercriminals"},{"time":97753,"text":"are wonderfully professional and organized."},{"time":101064,"text":"In fact, they have product adverts."},{"time":103935,"text":"You can go online and buy a hacking service"},{"time":106066,"text":"to knock your business competitor offline."},{"time":108215,"text":"Check out this one I found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109774,"text":"(Video) Man: So you're here for one reason,"},{"time":111593,"text":"and that reason is"},{"time":113058,"text":"because you need your business competitors,"},{"time":114970,"text":"rivals, haters, or whatever the reason is, or who,"},{"time":118922,"text":"they are to go down."},{"time":120666,"text":"Well you, my friend, you've came to the right place."},{"time":123526,"text":"If you want your business competitors to go down,"},{"time":125942,"text":"well, they can."},{"time":127278,"text":"If you want your rivals to go offline, well, they will."},{"time":130702,"text":"Not only that, we are providing a short-term-to-long-term"},{"time":133729,"text":"DDOS service or scheduled attack,"},{"time":136084,"text":"starting five dollars per hour for small personal websites"},{"time":139895,"text":"to 10 to 50 dollars per hour."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142799,"text":"James Lyne: Now, I did actually pay"},{"time":144122,"text":"one of these cybercriminals to attack my own website."},{"time":146915,"text":"Things got a bit tricky when I tried to expense it at the company."},{"time":150409,"text":"Turns out that's not cool."},{"time":152123,"text":"But regardless, it's amazing how many products"},{"time":155133,"text":"and services are available now to cybercriminals."},{"time":158245,"text":"For example, this testing platform,"},{"time":160721,"text":"which enables the cybercriminals"},{"time":162436,"text":"to test the quality of their viruses"},{"time":164918,"text":"before they release them on the world."},{"time":167370,"text":"For a small fee, they can upload it"},{"time":169327,"text":"and make sure everything is good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170993,"text":"But it goes further."},{"time":172526,"text":"Cybercriminals now have crime packs"},{"time":174771,"text":"with business intelligence reporting dashboards"},{"time":177890,"text":"to manage the distribution of their malicious code."},{"time":181366,"text":"This is the market leader in malware distribution,"},{"time":184894,"text":"the Black Hole Exploit Pack,"},{"time":186532,"text":"responsible for nearly one third of malware distribution"},{"time":190191,"text":"in the last couple of quarters."},{"time":192165,"text":"It comes with technical installation guides,"},{"time":195174,"text":"video setup routines,"},{"time":196219,"text":"and get this, technical support."},{"time":200174,"text":"You can email the cybercriminals and they'll tell you"},{"time":202562,"text":"how to set up your illegal hacking server."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206184,"text":"So let me show you what malicious code looks like today."},{"time":210468,"text":"What I've got here is two systems,"},{"time":212780,"text":"an attacker, which I've made look all Matrix-y and scary,"},{"time":216470,"text":"and a victim, which you might recognize from home or work."},{"time":219772,"text":"Now normally, these would be on different sides"},{"time":222501,"text":"of the planet or of the Internet,"},{"time":225056,"text":"but I've put them side by side"},{"time":226452,"text":"because it makes things much more interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229116,"text":"Now, there are many ways you can get infected."},{"time":231171,"text":"You will have come in contact with some of them."},{"time":233763,"text":"Maybe some of you have received an email"},{"time":235859,"text":"that says something like, \"Hi, I'm a Nigerian banker,"},{"time":239944,"text":"and I'd like to give you 53 billion dollars"},{"time":242708,"text":"because I like your face.\""},{"time":245135,"text":"Or funnycats.exe, which rumor has it"},{"time":248529,"text":"was quite successful in China's recent campaign against America."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252298,"text":"Now there are many ways you can get infected."},{"time":254728,"text":"I want to show you a couple of my favorites."},{"time":256715,"text":"This is a little USB key."},{"time":259375,"text":"Now how do you get a USB key to run in a business?"},{"time":261532,"text":"Well, you could try looking really cute."},{"time":265657,"text":"Awww."},{"time":267595,"text":"Or, in my case, awkward and pathetic."},{"time":269958,"text":"So imagine this scenario: I walk into one of your businesses,"},{"time":274147,"text":"looking very awkward and pathetic, with a copy of my C.V."},{"time":276989,"text":"which I've covered in coffee,"},{"time":278888,"text":"and I ask the receptionist to plug in this USB key"},{"time":282275,"text":"and print me a new one."},{"time":284224,"text":"So let's have a look here on my victim computer."},{"time":287454,"text":"What I'm going to do is plug in the USB key."},{"time":290700,"text":"After a couple of seconds,"},{"time":292190,"text":"things start to happen on the computer on their own,"},{"time":294941,"text":"usually a bad sign."},{"time":296876,"text":"This would, of course, normally happen"},{"time":298570,"text":"in a couple of seconds, really, really quickly,"},{"time":301328,"text":"but I've kind of slowed it down"},{"time":302988,"text":"so you can actually see the attack occurring."},{"time":305818,"text":"Malware is very boring otherwise."},{"time":308335,"text":"So this is writing out the malicious code,"},{"time":310932,"text":"and a few seconds later, on the left-hand side,"},{"time":314729,"text":"you'll see the attacker's screen get some interesting new text."},{"time":319027,"text":"Now if I place the mouse cursor over it,"},{"time":320958,"text":"this is what we call a command prompt,"},{"time":323265,"text":"and using this we can navigate around the computer."},{"time":327062,"text":"We can access your documents, your data."},{"time":329221,"text":"You can turn on the webcam."},{"time":330722,"text":"That can be very embarrassing."},{"time":332351,"text":"Or just to really prove a point,"},{"time":334074,"text":"we can launch programs like my personal favorite,"},{"time":337195,"text":"the Windows Calculator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"So isn't it amazing how much control"},{"time":342288,"text":"the attackers can get with such a simple operation?"},{"time":345183,"text":"Let me show you how most malware"},{"time":347114,"text":"is now distributed today."},{"time":349297,"text":"What I'm going to do is open up a website"},{"time":351817,"text":"that I wrote."},{"time":353133,"text":"It's a terrible website. It's got really awful graphics."},{"time":357448,"text":"And it's got a comments section here"},{"time":359642,"text":"where we can submit comments to the website."},{"time":363323,"text":"Many of you will have used something a bit like this before."},{"time":366330,"text":"Unfortunately, when this was implemented,"},{"time":368277,"text":"the developer was slightly inebriated"},{"time":370702,"text":"and managed to forget"},{"time":371944,"text":"all of the secure coding practices he had learned."},{"time":374933,"text":"So let's imagine that our attacker,"},{"time":377999,"text":"called Evil Hacker just for comedy value,"},{"time":381447,"text":"inserts something a little nasty."},{"time":383470,"text":"This is a script."},{"time":385169,"text":"It's code which will be interpreted on the webpage."},{"time":389246,"text":"So I'm going to submit this post,"},{"time":391571,"text":"and then, on my victim computer,"},{"time":393953,"text":"I'm going to open up the web browser"},{"time":395980,"text":"and browse to my website,"},{"time":398233,"text":"www.incrediblyhacked.com."},{"time":402022,"text":"Notice that after a couple of seconds,"},{"time":404146,"text":"I get redirected."},{"time":405603,"text":"That website address at the top there,"},{"time":407580,"text":"which you can just about see, microshaft.com,"},{"time":410911,"text":"the browser crashes as it hits one of these exploit packs,"},{"time":414104,"text":"and up pops fake antivirus."},{"time":418128,"text":"This is a virus pretending to look like antivirus software,"},{"time":423184,"text":"and it will go through and it will scan the system,"},{"time":425549,"text":"have a look at what its popping up here."},{"time":427057,"text":"It creates some very serious alerts."},{"time":428805,"text":"Oh look, a child porn proxy server."},{"time":431148,"text":"We really should clean that up."},{"time":433580,"text":"What's really insulting about this is"},{"time":435164,"text":"not only does it provide the attackers with access to your data,"},{"time":439402,"text":"but when the scan finishes, they tell you"},{"time":442225,"text":"in order to clean up the fake viruses,"},{"time":445348,"text":"you have to register the product."},{"time":448024,"text":"Now I liked it better when viruses were free."},{"time":451360,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":454139,"text":"People now pay cybercriminals money"},{"time":456665,"text":"to run viruses,"},{"time":458766,"text":"which I find utterly bizarre."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461527,"text":"So anyway, let me change pace a little bit."},{"time":465063,"text":"Chasing 250,000 pieces of malware a day"},{"time":468569,"text":"is a massive challenge,"},{"time":470224,"text":"and those numbers are only growing"},{"time":472294,"text":"directly in proportion to the length of my stress line, you'll note here."},{"time":476173,"text":"So I want to talk to you briefly"},{"time":478049,"text":"about a group of hackers we tracked for a year"},{"time":481099,"text":"and actually found --"},{"time":483106,"text":"and this is a rare treat in our job."},{"time":485683,"text":"Now this was a cross-industry collaboration,"},{"time":488166,"text":"people from Facebook, independent researchers,"},{"time":490555,"text":"guys from Sophos."},{"time":492636,"text":"So here we have a couple of documents"},{"time":495291,"text":"which our cybercriminals had uploaded"},{"time":498117,"text":"to a cloud service, kind of like Dropbox or SkyDrive,"},{"time":502494,"text":"like many of you might use."},{"time":504703,"text":"At the top, you'll notice a section of source code."},{"time":508095,"text":"What this would do is send the cybercriminals"},{"time":511063,"text":"a text message every day telling them how much money"},{"time":516103,"text":"they'd made that day,"},{"time":517769,"text":"so a kind of cybercriminal billings report, if you will."},{"time":521065,"text":"If you look closely, you'll notice a series"},{"time":523822,"text":"of what are Russian telephone numbers."},{"time":526805,"text":"Now that's obviously interesting,"},{"time":528284,"text":"because that gives us a way of finding our cybercriminals."},{"time":531521,"text":"Down below, highlighted in red,"},{"time":533636,"text":"in the other section of source code,"},{"time":535387,"text":"is this bit \"leded:leded.\""},{"time":538130,"text":"That's a username,"},{"time":539419,"text":"kind of like you might have on Twitter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542278,"text":"So let's take this a little further."},{"time":543509,"text":"There are a few other interesting pieces"},{"time":545767,"text":"the cybercriminals had uploaded."},{"time":548042,"text":"Lots of you here will use smartphones"},{"time":550614,"text":"to take photos and post them from the conference."},{"time":553261,"text":"An interesting feature of lots of modern smartphones"},{"time":556098,"text":"is that when you take a photo,"},{"time":557765,"text":"it embeds GPS data about where that photo was taken."},{"time":562002,"text":"In fact, I've been spending a lot of time"},{"time":564445,"text":"on Internet dating sites recently,"},{"time":566689,"text":"obviously for research purposes,"},{"time":569100,"text":"and I've noticed that about 60 percent"},{"time":572621,"text":"of the profile pictures on Internet dating sites"},{"time":575444,"text":"contain the GPS coordinates of where the photo was taken,"},{"time":579895,"text":"which is kind of scary"},{"time":580956,"text":"because you wouldn't give out your home address"},{"time":583518,"text":"to lots of strangers,"},{"time":584967,"text":"but we're happy to give away our GPS coordinates"},{"time":586961,"text":"to plus or minus 15 meters."},{"time":590990,"text":"And our cybercriminals had done the same thing."},{"time":594224,"text":"So here's a photo which resolves to St. Petersburg."},{"time":597428,"text":"We then deploy the incredibly advanced hacking tool."},{"time":601114,"text":"We used Google."},{"time":603509,"text":"Using the email address, the telephone number"},{"time":605734,"text":"and the GPS data, on the left you see an advert"},{"time":609283,"text":"for a BMW that one of our cybercriminals is selling,"},{"time":612952,"text":"on the other side an advert for the sale of sphynx kittens."},{"time":618300,"text":"One of these was more stereotypical for me."},{"time":621400,"text":"A little more searching, and here's our cybercriminal."},{"time":625389,"text":"Imagine, these are hardened cybercriminals"},{"time":628935,"text":"sharing information scarcely."},{"time":630803,"text":"Imagine what you could find"},{"time":631951,"text":"about each of the people in this room."},{"time":633654,"text":"A bit more searching through the profile"},{"time":635460,"text":"and there's a photo of their office."},{"time":637320,"text":"They were working on the third floor."},{"time":639368,"text":"And you can also see some photos"},{"time":641567,"text":"from his business companion"},{"time":642742,"text":"where he has a taste in a certain kind of image."},{"time":647581,"text":"It turns out he's a member of the Russian Adult Webmasters Federation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651576,"text":"But this is where our investigation starts to slow down."},{"time":654593,"text":"The cybercriminals have locked down their profiles quite well."},{"time":658536,"text":"And herein is the greatest lesson"},{"time":660571,"text":"of social media and mobile devices for all of us right now."},{"time":665149,"text":"Our friends, our families and our colleagues"},{"time":668879,"text":"can break our security even when we do the right things."},{"time":673568,"text":"This is MobSoft, one of the companies"},{"time":676348,"text":"that this cybercriminal gang owned,"},{"time":678514,"text":"and an interesting thing about MobSoft"},{"time":680103,"text":"is the 50-percent owner of this"},{"time":682974,"text":"posted a job advert,"},{"time":684921,"text":"and this job advert matched one of the telephone numbers"},{"time":688301,"text":"from the code earlier."},{"time":690453,"text":"This woman was Maria,"},{"time":692578,"text":"and Maria is the wife of one of our cybercriminals."},{"time":695458,"text":"And it's kind of like she went into her social media settings"},{"time":698978,"text":"and clicked on every option imaginable"},{"time":701773,"text":"to make herself really, really insecure."},{"time":705470,"text":"By the end of the investigation,"},{"time":707037,"text":"where you can read the full 27-page report at that link,"},{"time":710596,"text":"we had photos of the cybercriminals,"},{"time":712630,"text":"even the office Christmas party"},{"time":715525,"text":"when they were out on an outing."},{"time":717391,"text":"That's right, cybercriminals do have Christmas parties,"},{"time":720640,"text":"as it turns out."},{"time":722228,"text":"Now you're probably wondering what happened to these guys."},{"time":724463,"text":"Let me come back to that in just a minute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727400,"text":"I want to change pace to one last little demonstration,"},{"time":730147,"text":"a technique that is wonderfully simple and basic,"},{"time":734116,"text":"but is interesting in exposing how much information"},{"time":737181,"text":"we're all giving away,"},{"time":738957,"text":"and it's relevant because it applies to us as a TED audience."},{"time":743235,"text":"This is normally when people start kind of shuffling in their pockets"},{"time":745685,"text":"trying to turn their phones onto airplane mode desperately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749903,"text":"Many of you all know about the concept"},{"time":751589,"text":"of scanning for wireless networks."},{"time":753932,"text":"You do it every time you take out your iPhone or your Blackberry"},{"time":757333,"text":"and connect to something like TEDAttendees."},{"time":761353,"text":"But what you might not know"},{"time":763100,"text":"is that you're also beaming out a list of networks"},{"time":767851,"text":"you've previously connected to,"},{"time":770273,"text":"even when you're not using wireless actively."},{"time":774420,"text":"So I ran a little scan."},{"time":776147,"text":"I was relatively inhibited compared to the cybercriminals,"},{"time":779073,"text":"who wouldn't be so concerned by law,"},{"time":781617,"text":"and here you can see my mobile device."},{"time":784204,"text":"Okay? So you can see a list of wireless networks."},{"time":786858,"text":"TEDAttendees, HyattLB. Where do you think I'm staying?"},{"time":791485,"text":"My home network, PrettyFlyForAWifi,"},{"time":794978,"text":"which I think is a great name."},{"time":796743,"text":"Sophos_Visitors, SANSEMEA, companies I work with."},{"time":799510,"text":"Loganwifi, that's in Boston. HiltonLondon."},{"time":802818,"text":"CIASurveillanceVan."},{"time":805259,"text":"We called it that at one of our conferences"},{"time":806868,"text":"because we thought that would freak people out,"},{"time":808604,"text":"which is quite fun."},{"time":810598,"text":"This is how geeks party."}]},{"cues":[{"time":815256,"text":"So let's make this a little bit more interesting."},{"time":817463,"text":"Let's talk about you."},{"time":820001,"text":"Twenty-three percent of you have been to Starbucks"},{"time":822111,"text":"recently and used the wireless network."},{"time":825226,"text":"Things get more interesting."},{"time":826390,"text":"Forty-six percent of you I could link to a business,"},{"time":828836,"text":"XYZ Employee network."},{"time":831706,"text":"This isn't an exact science, but it gets pretty accurate."},{"time":835885,"text":"Seven hundred and sixty-one of you I could identify a hotel you'd been to recently,"},{"time":840354,"text":"absolutely with pinpoint precision somewhere on the globe."},{"time":844193,"text":"Two hundred and thirty-four of you, well, I know where you live."},{"time":848141,"text":"Your wireless network name is so unique"},{"time":850460,"text":"that I was able to pinpoint it"},{"time":852009,"text":"using data available openly on the Internet"},{"time":854676,"text":"with no hacking or clever, clever tricks."},{"time":858924,"text":"And I should mention as well that"},{"time":860744,"text":"some of you do use your names,"},{"time":862286,"text":"\"James Lyne's iPhone,\" for example."},{"time":864882,"text":"And two percent of you have a tendency to extreme profanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":869240,"text":"So something for you to think about:"},{"time":871244,"text":"As we adopt these new applications and mobile devices,"},{"time":875157,"text":"as we play with these shiny new toys,"},{"time":877474,"text":"how much are we trading off convenience"},{"time":881296,"text":"for privacy and security?"},{"time":884186,"text":"Next time you install something,"},{"time":886244,"text":"look at the settings and ask yourself,"},{"time":888548,"text":"\"Is this information that I want to share?"},{"time":892100,"text":"Would someone be able to abuse it?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":894990,"text":"We also need to think very carefully"},{"time":897062,"text":"about how we develop our future talent pool."},{"time":901203,"text":"You see, technology's changing at a staggering rate,"},{"time":904182,"text":"and that 250,000 pieces of malware"},{"time":907358,"text":"won't stay the same for long."},{"time":910230,"text":"There's a very concerning trend"},{"time":912428,"text":"that whilst many people coming out of schools now"},{"time":915621,"text":"are much more technology-savvy, they know how to use technology,"},{"time":920033,"text":"fewer and fewer people are following the feeder subjects"},{"time":923646,"text":"to know how that technology works under the covers."},{"time":927970,"text":"In the U.K., a 60 percent reduction since 2003,"},{"time":932355,"text":"and there are similar statistics all over the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":936130,"text":"We also need to think about the legal issues in this area."},{"time":940206,"text":"The cybercriminals I talked about,"},{"time":941733,"text":"despite theft of millions of dollars,"},{"time":943872,"text":"actually still haven't been arrested,"},{"time":945981,"text":"and at this point possibly never will."},{"time":949540,"text":"Most laws are national in their implementation,"},{"time":953040,"text":"despite cybercrime conventions, where the Internet"},{"time":957039,"text":"is borderless and international by definition."},{"time":960145,"text":"Countries do not agree, which makes this area"},{"time":962978,"text":"exceptionally challenging from a legal perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":966595,"text":"But my biggest ask is this:"},{"time":970955,"text":"You see, you're going to leave here"},{"time":972597,"text":"and you're going to see some astonishing stories in the news."},{"time":976314,"text":"You're going to read about malware doing incredible"},{"time":978488,"text":"and terrifying, scary things."},{"time":981749,"text":"However, 99 percent of it works"},{"time":985678,"text":"because people fail to do the basics."},{"time":989868,"text":"So my ask is this: Go online,"},{"time":992890,"text":"find these simple best practices,"},{"time":995535,"text":"find out how to update and patch your computer."},{"time":998089,"text":"Get a secure password."},{"time":999640,"text":"Make sure you use a different password"},{"time":1001170,"text":"on each of your sites and services online."},{"time":1004521,"text":"Find these resources. Apply them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1007764,"text":"The Internet is a fantastic resource"},{"time":1010375,"text":"for business, for political expression,"},{"time":1012440,"text":"for art and for learning."},{"time":1014771,"text":"Help me and the security community"},{"time":1017953,"text":"make life much, much more difficult"},{"time":1021421,"text":"for cybercriminals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1023373,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1024701,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}